@@TJvWizardRouteMapList
<TITLEIMG TJvWizardRouteMapList>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.Wizards.RouteMaps
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A route map component that displays the pages of a wizard as a list.
Description
  Use TJvWizardRouteMapList to display the pages in a TJvWizard as a list of items.
  TJvWizardRouteMapList has several properties to control its appearance and behavior, including
  Clickable, Alignment, ShowImages, HotTrack, ItemColor, ItemHeight and many others.

  To use this component, you should:

  * Drop a TJvWizard on the form.
  * Select the wizard in the form.
  * Drop a TJvWizardRouteMapList on the wizard.

